body: "## Audit #14 scope & method (2026-07-06)\nFull pass over 1,634 items (147→148 open after new finding, 12→3 in_progress after reset, 1,463 closed, 12 canceled legit archives/probes).\n\n## Verified green\n- Orphans: zero (only root milestone pm-doxj is parentless, by design) — checked via direct .agents/pm TOON grep (unquoted 'status:' format).\n- Every validate warning maps to exactly one open item: 18 close_reason + 269 resolution → pm-e9zh; 146 missing / 134 orphaned linked files → pm-j8z6; GH-209 duplicate issue code → pm-pivf.\n- pm health green: 1,634 vector-ledger entries, 0 stale.\n- Roadmap milestone pm-doxj indexes all 13 capability epics + 3 initiatives (pm-n7rr, pm-usfg, pm-9rxu) with horizon ordering; composability set pm-m9xv/pm-646c/pm-psy1 present.\n- Head commit dc0dc252 fully covered by audit #13 (pm-lgim); no untracked code/feature work found (only open PRs are 3 dependabot bumps).\n\n## Gap found & fixed\nDocstring initiative pm-4ak1 + 8 child tasks were phantom in_progress since 07-04/05: no claim, no branch, no PR, no commits. Reverted family to open (comment on pm-4ak1); remaining in_progress is genuine (pm-rjqr landed partial work in 9c909a58 today; pm-lt6n awaits Windows nightly oracle; pm-92if living epic).\n\n## New backlog item\npm-w8q4 (Feature, under pm-dj98): stale in-progress detection — validate/health warn on unclaimed+inactive in_progress items + advisory on unclaimed status flips. Dedup-checked (stale/abandoned/claim/lease/heartbeat searches)."
